cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper discusses video description, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also focuses on deep learning models, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses evaluation metrics, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
